Growth of L. mesenteroides KKP 389 and F. tropaeoli KKP 3032 on GYP agar under aerobic (left) and anaerobic (right) conditions. 1,3 - L. mesenteroides KKP 389; 2,4 - F. tropaeoli KKP 3032

